      <li>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>


  <section id="about">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-user icon"></i>
    <p class="intro">
      Fueled by a personal commitment to learning and growth, I have found a love for the ever-evolving world of software. For me, programming sits at the intersection of creativity, methodical thinking, and steep learning curves, providing the perfect challenge. Whether it's building custom solutions or diving into new frameworks, each obstacle gives a new opportunity to innovate and invent.
    </p>

    <div class="tech-stack">
      <div class="tech">
        <%= image_tag "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f1/Ruby_logo.png", :alt => "ruby-logo"%>
        <p>Ruby</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech">
        <%= image_tag "https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/027/127/463/non_2x/javascript-logo-javascript-icon-transparent-free-png.png", :alt=>"javascript-logo"%>
        <p>Javascript</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech">
        <%= image_tag "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c3/Python-logo-notext.svg/1200px-Python-logo-notext.svg.png" , :alt => "python-logo"%>
        <p>Python</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech">
        <%= image_tag "https://cdn.iconscout.com/icon/free/png-256/free-html-5-logo-icon-download-in-svg-png-gif-file-formats--programming-langugae-language-pack-logos-icons-1175208.png", :alt => "HTML-logo"%>
        <p>HTML</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech">
        <%= image_tag "https://sass-lang.com/assets/img/styleguide/seal-color.png", :alt => "SCSS-logo"%>
        <p>SCSS</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech">
        <%= image_tag "https://huyza.gallerycdn.vsassets.io/extensions/huyza/dax-language/0.0.2/1628621363691/Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.Icons.Default", :alt => "DAX-logo"%>
        <p>DAX</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tech">
        <%= image_tag "https://static.wixstatic.com/media/816382_bd664a10b4ec4239b7f9739dbd210863~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_420,h_420,al_c,lg_1,q_85/816382_bd664a10b4ec4239b7f9739dbd210863~mv2.png", :alt => "PowerFX-logo"%>
        <p>PowerFX</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= link_to "More about me", "#background", class: "button-secondary toggle", id: "show-toggle"%>
    <%= link_to "Less about me", "#about", class: "button-secondary toggle", id: "hide-toggle", style: "display: none;"%>

    <div id="background" style="display: none;">
      <h3> Background </h3>
      <p>
        Hello! I am Leon, an enthusiastic career changer with three years experience in supply chain, geering up to focus my expertise and data background into development. In my career so far, I have discovered the key to my professional fulfillment is continuous learning. When I first encountered programming, using R for statistical analysis in my Economics degree, I spent hours beyond the scope of the course creating descriptive statistics visuals. The ability to translate intricate information into digestible material opened the gateway for my love of code.
      </p>
      <p>
        Fast forward to my career in supply chain, I began with data analytics using DAX and SQL and three years later ended up building my first custom platform for internal use. Over the following 4 months I developed three platforms and began collaborating with other business functions across sales, finance and operations to support their diverse needs.
      </p>
      <p>
        Having little resources and relying heavily on my own curiosity and research ability was energising and ultimately ignited my move into software engineering. Landing me where I am today, with 450+ hours of coding under my belt and a BCS-accredited certificate in Web Development with AI, I am excited to focus my unique operational perspective into a dynamic development team where I can continue learning and have an impact.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section id="projects">
    <h3>Projects</h3>

    <div class="project project-left">
      <%= image_tag "property-sphere.png", :alt => "property-sphere-landing-page"%>
      <div class="project-info">
        <h4>Property Sphere</h4>
        <p>A centralised search and organisational tool that scrapes major sites and leverages location APIs to offer advanced filtering</p>
        <%= link_to "Live App", "https://property-sphere-f0c399e44756.herokuapp.com/", :class => "button-primary"%>
        <%= link_to "Learn More", "https://github.com/LeonBrimacombe/property-sphere", :class => "button-secondary"%>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project project-right">
      <div class="project-info">
        <h4>Tool Shared</h4>
        <p>A market place for users to list and rent tools in their local area</p>
        <%= link_to "Live App", "", :class => "button-primary"%>
        <%= link_to "Learn More", "https://github.com/LeonBrimacombe/tool-shared", :class => "button-secondary"%>
      </div>
      <%= image_tag "tool-shared.jpg", :alt => "tool-shared-landing-page"%>
    </div>

    <div class="project project-left">
      <%= image_tag "tool-shared.jpg", :alt => "tool-shared-landing-page"%>
      <div class="project-info">
        <h4>Sales Profitability Calculator</h4>
        <div>
          <p>A customer-facing sales tool displaying profit comparisons for home versus competitor brands.</p>
          <p>Used across a 45-person sales team, team member inputs populate a sales agreement, that is signed and emailed to customer in-app. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project project-right">
      <div class="project-info">
        <h4>Stock Ordering Portal</h4>
        <p>A internal stock ordering portal that takes customer orders and output details in an email to the fulfilment team.</p>
      </div>
      <%= image_tag "tool-shared.jpg", :alt => "tool-shared-landing-page"%>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="wips">
    <h3>Works in Progress</h3>
    <div class="wips">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-clipboard-check icon"></i>
      <p>Currently working on a freelance Python platform with Django showing users their homes energy consumption accessed via In-home Dispay (IHD) APIs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>If you you would like to know more or want to work together, you can leave me your details to start a conversation. </p>
    <%= form_with scope: :contact_form, url: contact_form_index_path, method: :post, local: true, class: "container contact", id: "contact-form" do |form| %>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= form.text_field :name, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Name" %>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= form.email_field :email, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Email" %>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= form.text_area :message, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Message" %>
      </div>
      <%= form.submit "Submit", class: "button-secondary" %>
    <% end %>
  </section>

  <section id="footer">
    <div class="socials">
      <a class="link-icons" href="https://github.com/LeonBrimacombe" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i></a>
      <a class="link-icons" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lbrimacombe/" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i></a>
    </div>
    <p>LEON BRIMACOMBE ©2024</p>
  </section>
</div>
